Arch - Homesystem

"Base-System Installation
https://www.tecmint.com/arch-linux-installation-and-configuration-guide/"

- Herunterladen und mit Etcher auf Stick flashen
  "https://www.archlinux.de/download
  https://www.balena.io/etcher/"
- Netzwerk anh√§ngen und DHCP starten
  "dhcpcd						# Startet dhcp-client
  ping google.com				# Check if network connected üï∏"
- Grundkonfiguration
  "loadkeys de_CH-latin1 			# Load swiss keyboard
  pacman -Sy					# Update package üì¶ list"
- Partitionierung
  "cfdisk /dev/sda				# Start partitioning tool üõ†
  # Make sure that gpt is showed on top
  # Delete all partitions with ‚Üë‚Üì‚Üê‚Üí [enter]
  # Create following partitions:
  #   1- 300M size, EFI System type
  #   2- 8G size, Linux swap type
  #   3 - Remaining space-size, Linux filesystem type
  # Now write, type yes and quit"
- Dateisysteme erstellen, mounten
  "mkfs.fat -F32 /dev/sda1			# Create EFI-Filesystem
  mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda3			# Create main filesystem
  mkswap /dev/sda2				# Create swap filesystem
  mount /dev/sda3 /mnt			# Mount main partition
  swapon /dev/sda2				# Enable swap"
- Basissystem installieren
  "pacstrap /mnt base base-devel	# Install basic packages
  # Generate mount script for disks
  genfstab -U -p /mnt >> /mnt/etc/fstab"
- Systemkonfiguration
  "arch-chroot /mnt				# Login to new system
  echo "eda-wipe" > /etc/hostname	# Set hostname
  pacman -S vim					# Install vim
  vim /etc/locale.gen				# File with locales
  # uncomment all needed languages and save file (de_CH.UTF-8)
  locale-gen					# Generate selected locales
  echo LANG=de_CH.UTF-8 > /etc/locale.conf
  # Set locale time to zurich
  ln -s /usr/share/zoneinfo/Europe/Zurich /etc/localtime
  hwclock --systohc --utc			# Set hardware clock
  vim /etc/pacman.conf			# Uncomment [multilib] and line below
  passwd [enter] edawipe19		# Set password
  # Add a non-admin user
  useradd -mg users -G wheel,storage,power -s /bin/bash install
  passwd install [enter] install
  # Give install ability to execute root commands
  pacman -S sudo
  vim /etc/sudoers				#  copy line with "root" and change to "install"
  cat << EOF >> /etc/vconsole.conf	# Set swiss keyboard as default
  KEYMAP=de_CH-latin1
  EOF"
- Bootloader
  "# Install packets and mount efi-drive
  pacman -S grub efibootmgr dosfstools os-prober mtools
  mkdir /boot/EFI
  mount /dev/sda1 /boot/EFI		# If not working reboot
  # Install an efi-grub
  grub-install --target=x86_64-efi  --bootloader-id=grub_uefi --recheck
  grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg"
- Exit - Installation abgeschlossen
  "exit
  umount -a
  telinit 6"
- BIOS-Korrektur
  "Ins BIOS mit F2 gehen.
  Dort "Add Boot Option"
  Danach navigieren bis GRUB gefunden wird
  Namen hinzuf√ºgen und "Add" klicken, als Prio festlegen"
- Im Neuen System
  "systemctl start dhcpcd
  systemctl enable dhcpcd
  ping google.com
  "
